- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The proposed method involves the use of linear least-squares regression and neural networks, which are common machine learning techniques. 
- cs.DS (Discrete Mathematics): The paper deals with the analysis of dynamical systems, which can be modeled using discrete mathematics. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of neural networks in the proposed method falls under the category of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed implementation of the method using neural networks falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing.
